Introduction

RESCENE is a five-member girl group under THE MUZE Entertainment. They released their pre-release single "YoYo" on the 29th of February and made their official debut on March 26, 2024 with the single album "Re:Scene" with "UhUh" serving as the single's title track.

The group name comes from their motto : recalling the scene through the scent.

On July 10, 2024, they announced their official fandom name, "REMINE", which is a play on the word "REMIND" and a word that combines RESCENE and MINE. It means that RESCENE is an eternal scent and scene that fans will never forget.
